"tlg0656_tlg001.T214145" [label=<<b>THESIS</b><br/>     Dioscorides-Pedanius     <br/>5.88.4 (of <i>div</i>)<br/><i>The operations described above {i.e., in the 1st<br/>recipe for lead white, in the 2nd recipe for lead<br/>white, and in the 1st recipe for shaping lead<br/>white (into lozenges)} should be accomplished in<br/>summer<br/></i><font point-size="12">"θέρους μέντοι ἐργαστέον τὰ προειρημένα"</font>>, gephi_label="THES", locus="5.88.4_div", speaker="Dioscorides-Pedanius", text="θέρους μέντοι ἐργαστέον τὰ προειρημένα", paraphrasis="The operations described above {i.e., in the 1st recipe for lead white, in the 2nd recipe for lead white, and in the 1st recipe for shaping lead white (into lozenges)} should be accomplished in summer ", manifestation="explicit", source="tlg0656_tlg001", fillcolor="#f0faf0", color="#82b366", style="rounded,filled", shape="box", margin="0.30,0.1"];

