"tlg0656_tlg001.T193924" [label=<<b>THESIS</b><br/>     Dioscorides-Pedanius     <br/>5.88.4 (of <i>div</i>)<br/><i>( (White and effective) lead white ) is also<br/>prepared in winter: ( .(In winter,) one does the<br/>same as in {phases 1 to 7 of the 1st recipe for<br/>lead white} OR as in {phases 1.1-5.1 of the 2nd<br/>recipe for lead white} ), .One places the jars<br/>(i.e., each vessel after the viscous fluid has<br/>been poured inside it) on top of the furnaces of<br/>baths OR (regular) furnaces (and lets their<br/>content dry), (. One does the same as in phases 9<br/>to 13 of the 1st recipe for lead white} OR as in<br/>{phases 7.1 of the 2nd recipe for lead white} )<br/></i><font point-size="12">"σκευάζεται δὲ καὶ ... ἢ καμίνων"</font>>, gephi_label="THES", locus="5.88.4_div", speaker="Dioscorides-Pedanius", text="σκευάζεται δὲ καὶ χειμῶνος, τῶν πιθακνῶν ὑπεράνω τῶν ἰπνῶν τῶν βαλανείων τιθεμένων ἢ καμίνων", paraphrasis="( (White and effective) lead white ) is also prepared in winter: ( .(In winter,) one does the same as in {phases 1 to 7 of the 1st recipe for lead white} OR as in {phases 1.1-5.1 of the 2nd recipe for lead white} ), .One places the jars (i.e., each vessel after the viscous fluid has been poured inside it) on top of the furnaces of baths OR (regular) furnaces (and lets their content dry), (. One does the same as in phases 9 to 13 of the 1st recipe for lead white} OR as in {phases 7.1 of the 2nd recipe for lead white} ) ", manifestation="explicit", source="tlg0656_tlg001", fillcolor="#f0faf0", color="#82b366", style="rounded,filled", shape="box", margin="0.30,0.1"];

"tlg0656_tlg001.T193924_referenced-in_tlg0656_tlg001.T235335_1" [label=<IS REFERENCED IN>, fontsize="11", style="rounded,filled", fillcolor="#f0f3e0", color="#708238", shape="note"];

"tlg0656_tlg001.T205232" [label=<<b>THESIS</b><br/>     Dioscorides-Pedanius     <br/>5.88.4 (of <i>div</i>)<br/><i>( (White and effective) lead white ) is also<br/>shaped (into lozenges) in winter: ( .(In winter,)<br/>one does the same as in {phases 1 to 2 of the 1st<br/>recipe for shaping lead white (into lozenges), )<br/>(. One puts the lead white kneaded with vinegar<br/>and made into shapes inside jars) .One places the<br/>jars on top of the furnaces of baths OR (regular)<br/>furnaces (and leaves their content to dry)<br/></i><font point-size="12">"θέρους μέντοι ἐργαστέον ... ἢ καμίνων"</font>>, gephi_label="THES", locus="5.88.4_div", speaker="Dioscorides-Pedanius", text="θέρους μέντοι ἐργαστέον τὰ προειρημένα ... σκευάζεται δὲ καὶ χειμῶνος, τῶν πιθακνῶν ὑπεράνω τῶν ἰπνῶν τῶν βαλανείων τιθεμένων ἢ καμίνων", paraphrasis="( (White and effective) lead white ) is also shaped (into lozenges) in winter: ( .(In winter,) one does the same as in {phases 1 to 2 of the 1st recipe for shaping lead white (into lozenges), ) (. One puts the lead white kneaded with vinegar and made into shapes inside jars) .One places the jars on top of the furnaces of baths OR (regular) furnaces (and leaves their content to dry) ", manifestation="explicit", source="tlg0656_tlg001", fillcolor="#f0faf0", color="#82b366", style="rounded,filled", shape="box", margin="0.30,0.1"];

"tlg0656_tlg001.T205232_referenced-in_tlg0656_tlg001.T235335_1" [label=<IS REFERENCED IN>, fontsize="11", style="rounded,filled", fillcolor="#f0f3e0", color="#708238", shape="note"];

"tlg0656_tlg001.T235335" [label=<<b>impl. THESIS</b><br/>     Dioscorides-Pedanius     <br/>5.88.4 (of <i>div</i>)<br/><i>( In the winter recipes for lead white and for<br/>shaping lead white (into lozenges), placing the<br/>jars on top of the furnaces of baths OR (regular)<br/>furnaces instead of under the summer sun is an<br/>equally appropriate solution )<br/></i><font point-size="12">"θέρους μέντοι ἐργαστέον ... τῷ ἡλίῳ"</font>>, gephi_label="THES", locus="5.88.4_div", speaker="Dioscorides-Pedanius", text="θέρους μέντοι ἐργαστέον τὰ προειρημένα ... σκευάζεται δὲ καὶ χειμῶνος, τῶν πιθακνῶν ὑπεράνω τῶν ἰπνῶν τῶν βαλανείων τιθεμένων ἢ καμίνων · ἡ γὰρ ἀναφερομένη θερμασία τὸ αὐτὸ δρᾷ τῷ ἡλίῳ", paraphrasis="( In the winter recipes for lead white and for shaping lead white (into lozenges), placing the jars on top of the furnaces of baths OR (regular) furnaces instead of under the summer sun is an equally appropriate solution ) ", manifestation="implicit", source="tlg0656_tlg001", fillcolor="#fcfffd", color="#666666", style="rounded,filled,dashed", shape="box", margin="0.30,0.1"];

"tlg0656_tlg001.T000509" [label=<<b>THESIS</b><br/>     Dioscorides-Pedanius     <br/>5.88.4 (of <i>div</i>)<br/><i>The heat rising up (from the furnaces of the baths<br/>and from regular furnaces) has the same effect<br/>(over the processes for producing lead white and<br/>for shaping lead white) as the (summer) sun<br/></i><font point-size="12">"θέρους μέντοι ἐργαστέον ... τῷ ἡλίῳ"</font>>, gephi_label="THES", locus="5.88.4_div", speaker="Dioscorides-Pedanius", text="θέρους μέντοι ἐργαστέον τὰ προειρημένα ... σκευάζεται δὲ καὶ χειμῶνος, τῶν πιθακνῶν ὑπεράνω τῶν ἰπνῶν τῶν βαλανείων τιθεμένων ἢ καμίνων · ἡ γὰρ ἀναφερομένη θερμασία τὸ αὐτὸ δρᾷ τῷ ἡλίῳ", paraphrasis="The heat rising up (from the furnaces of the baths and from regular furnaces) has the same effect (over the processes for producing lead white and for shaping lead white) as the (summer) sun ", manifestation="explicit", source="tlg0656_tlg001", fillcolor="#f0faf0", color="#82b366", style="rounded,filled", shape="box", margin="0.30,0.1"];

"tlg0656_tlg001.S002022" [label=<<b>SUPPORT</b><br/>     Dioscorides-Pedanius     <br/>5.88.4 (of <i>div</i>)<br/><i>form: particular-illustration</i><br/><font point-size="12">"ἡ γὰρ ἀναφερομένη ... τῷ ἡλίῳ"</font>>, gephi_label="SUPP", text="ἡ γὰρ ἀναφερομένη θερμασία τὸ αὐτὸ δρᾷ τῷ ἡλίῳ", locus="5.88.4_div", speaker="Dioscorides-Pedanius", form="particular-illustration", paraphrasis="\"The heat rising up (from the furnaces of the baths and from regular furnaces) has the same effect (over the processes for producing lead white and for shaping lead white) as the (summer) sun\" EXPLAINS/justifies) \"( In the winter recipes for lead white and for shaping lead white (into lozenges), placing the jars on top of the furnaces of baths OR (regular) furnaces instead of under the summer sun is an equally appropriate solution )\" ", manifestation="explicit", fillcolor="#edffc4", color="#927b89", style="filled", shape="ellipse", margin="0.05,0.02", source="tlg0656_tlg001"];

