"tlg0656_tlg001.T155024" [label=<<b>THESIS</b><br/>     Dioscorides-Pedanius     <br/>5.88.4 (of <i>div</i>)<br/><i>Those which must be considered the best varieties<br/>(of lead white) (for its medical uses) are that<br/>prepared in Rhodes, that prepared in Corinth, or<br/>that made in Lacedaemon; that from Dicaiarchia is<br/>second to these<br/></i><font point-size="12">"κάλλιστον δὲ ἡγητέον ... ἐκ Δικαιαρχίας"</font>>, gephi_label="THES", locus="5.88.4_div", speaker="Dioscorides-Pedanius", text="κάλλιστον δὲ ἡγητέον τὸ ἐν Ῥόδῳ σκευασθὲν ἢ ἐν Κορίνθῳ ἢ ἐν Λακεδαίμονι, δευτερεύει δὲ τὸ ἐκ Δικαιαρχίας", paraphrasis="Those which must be considered the best varieties (of lead white) (for its medical uses) are that prepared in Rhodes, that prepared in Corinth, or that made in Lacedaemon; that from Dicaiarchia is second to these ", manifestation="explicit", source="tlg0656_tlg001", fillcolor="#f0faf0", color="#82b366", style="rounded,filled", shape="box", margin="0.30,0.1"];

"tlg0656_tlg001.T161627" [label=<<b>THESIS</b><br/>     Dioscorides-Pedanius     <br/>5.88.6 (of <i>div</i>)<br/><i>(Lead white)'s property is: cooling,<br/>adhesive-malleability-inducing, softening,<br/>filling, thinning, moderately controlling of<br/>excrescences, and – when mixed with cerates, fatty<br/>plasters and lozenges – cicatrising<br/></i><font point-size="12">"δύναμιν δὲ ἔχει ... καὶ τροχίσκοις"</font>>, gephi_label="THES", locus="5.88.6_div", speaker="Dioscorides-Pedanius", text="δύναμιν δὲ ἔχει ψυκτικήν, ἐμπλαστικήν, μαλακτικήν, πληρωτικήν, λεπτυντικήν, ἔτι δὲ πράως κατασταλτικὴν ὑπεροχῶν καὶ κατουλωτικήν, μειγνύμενον κηρωταῖς καὶ λιπαραῖς ἐμπλάστροις καὶ τροχίσκοις", paraphrasis="(Lead white)'s property is: cooling, adhesive-malleability-inducing, softening, filling, thinning, moderately controlling of excrescences, and – when mixed with cerates, fatty plasters and lozenges – cicatrising ", manifestation="explicit", source="tlg0656_tlg001", fillcolor="#f0faf0", color="#82b366", style="rounded,filled", shape="box", margin="0.30,0.1"];

